  {
    "title": "Story",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Prince of the Empire who was kidnapped and use by the Abyss\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Prince of the Moniyan Empire, raised by Alice and Thamuz after being kidnapped.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Moniyan Empire"
              },
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Alice"
              },
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Thamuz"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "He won a duel witnessed by Thamuz."
          },
          {
            "text": "After the conflict between Light and Dark, the Son of Darkness was about to represent the lord of the Abyss and lead the Abyssal Army to the [battlefront].",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Abyss"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
