  {
    "title": "Lore",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Twelve years ago, a prince was born in the Moniyan Empire.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Moniyan Empire"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "He was a symbol of salvation and justice for his people."
          },
          {
            "text": "It was believed that he would lead the Moniyan Empire in unifying the Land of Dawn."
          },
          {
            "text": "The Empire Nobles gave everything to the prince."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "On the day of prince's first birthday[,] he was found dead in his baby bed blanketed in blood."
          },
          {
            "text": "The room was covered with claw marks and the guards in charge of protecting the prince were also found dead."
          },
          {
            "text": "Sorrow engulfed the whole Moniyan Empire."
          },
          {
            "text": "The hope of the Empire had fallen and, to this day, there has never been such an inspiring prince."
          },
          {
            "text": "Some people believed the prince was killed by the Demons, while others still hoped the Prince was alive."
          },
          {
            "text": "The Empire Nobles appointed the Imperial Knights and the Monastery of Light to find out the truth."
          },
          {
            "text": "At the same time, the Son of Darkness was \"born\" too…"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "After several years, something strange appeared in the Southern Hills of the Moniyan Empire."
          },
          {
            "text": "In the deepest part of the Abyss, Thamuz, the Lord Lava, watched a special battle.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Abyss"
              },
              {
                "text": "Thamuz, the Lord Lava",
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Thamuz"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "In this glorious battle, the monsters fought with each other until the strongest emerged."
          },
          {
            "text": "He not only possessed the best Evil Gene but also proved to be the strongest fighter in the Demons."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Alice embraced the beloved fighter and recalled the \"Royal Plan\" that she had carried out.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Alice"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "He was a masterpiece for her."
          },
          {
            "text": "He mastered Alice's trick, deception, and military strategy."
          },
          {
            "text": "He also learned combat from Thamuz."
          },
          {
            "text": "Now, the Son of Darkness is a capable assistant for the Abyss."
          },
          {
            "text": "He will represent the Lord of the Abyss, fighting against the Moniyan Empire, implementing the \"Dawn Plan\", and destroying the \"Shining Spark\" of the Empire."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
